- apply
    - apply status onto target (onto team, other operator, self, enemy)
    - infliction (onto enemy)
- inflict
    - apply an infliction
- react
    - inflictions interacting with other inflictions/physical mechanics
- consume
    - skills can consume infliction to apply certain statuses
    - skills can consume reaction to apply certain statuses
- expend
    - use a resource and decrease its meter
- recover
    - increases a resource meter
- return
    - refunds a portion of resource expended
    - note: this is NOT equivalent to recover for game mechanic logic
- build
    - increases a gauge or resource